<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM3.8">
<l>pēya rēyeṉak kiyāvarum yāṉumōr</l>
<l>pēya ṉēyevark kumitu pēciyeṉ</l>
<l>ṉāya ṉēyaraṅ kāveṉṟa ḻaikkiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>pēya ṉāyoḻin tēṉempi rāṉukkē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Everyone is a demon to me, and I too am a demon to everyone. Why speak of it?</l>
<l>I am calling out saying, ‘O Cowherd! O Raṅga!’</l>
<l>I have ended up becoming a demon of our Lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
